<br>
Have fun!!<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=berdug0>berdug0</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(5/16/01 8:10:19 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: First stop...</span><hr size=1> At 26 I was still getting exp from the evil eye in Beholder even though they are green.<br>
<br>
At 27, the evil eyes don't give exp but the Lords (Sviir and Syrkl) still do.<br>
<br>
For the Lone Wizard, this is the safest camp.  I suggest you milk the eyes until they totally don't give exp anymore.  Plus the loot they drop isn't too bad.  I have more than enough money at current level to buy my level 29 spells.  Good luck. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm19.showMessage?topicID=56.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm19.showMessage?topicID=65.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm19.emailToFriend?topicID=61.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm19.threadControl?topicID=61.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm19.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=61.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm19.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=61.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub23.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm1">General Discussion<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm3">Trade Forum<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm4">Rant Forum<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfr